  <paragraph l10n="U" role="paragraph" id="par_id3150499" xml-lang="en-US" oldref="2"><variable id="typotext">Defines the properties for additional languages.</variable></paragraph>
  <paragraph xml-lang="en-US" oldref="3" role="note" id="par_id3153665" l10n="U">The <emph>Search Options for Japanese</emph> and <emph>Asian Layout</emph> tab pages are only visible if the <emph>Asian language support</emph> option in the <emph>Languages</emph> tab page is activated and the <emph>Options</emph> dialog is re-opened. The <emph>Complex Text Layout</emph> tab page is only visible if the <emph>CTL support</emph> is enabled.</paragraph>
